{"tid":1847990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日林鄭記者會總結:自求多福","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T09:20:06.000Z","uid":38528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99e8b2587363378713f7f3011712b7318fcba58a","tid":1847990,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"不封關,不停市,不作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfe166dddec30fd4276fd13f1170d4c4d4f3c7a","tid":1847990,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:19:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思阻大家少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但事關重大，請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懇求大家盡快無限期三罷</span><br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fEievG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fEievG.jpg&h=ea5edc6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COPqDXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOPqDXm.jpg&h=e479048d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服「要死一起死」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQ3Gchn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQ3Gchn.jpg&h=8f4e3e83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afd69e356e55e9a25a1cc1270fc52b891d106776","tid":1847990,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:19:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！